<h2>Other mandatory or suggested software</h2>
<ul>
  <li><a href="http://www.python.org">Python</a>: <b>prerequisite</b>
  for Leaf. Leaf is currently developed and tested on
  Python <b>2.7.2</b>. The Python 3 version of Leaf has not been
  thoroughly tested at the moment but seems to work.
  <li><a href="http://www.graphviz.org">Graphviz</a>: <b>required</b>
  for the <i>publish</i> and <i>export</i> Leaf features. Make sure
  that you can correctly run the "dot" command from a prompt.</li>
  <li><a href="http://www.scipy.org/">SciPy</a>: suggested scientific
  programming modules for Python.</li>
  <li><a href="http://rpy.sourceforge.net">Rpy</a>: suggested as
  Python to R interface.</li>
  <li><a href="http://www.r-project.org/">R</a>: the R language for
  scientific programming.</li>
</ul>

